#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:89 8f83d38310a3409184d49ccb87a8b6d3
msgid ""
"Path to a reference audio clip from the **same speaker**. When present, "
"the training sequence is constructed as ``[103, ref_feats, 104, text, "
"101, audio_feats, 102]``, teaching the model to clone the speaker's voice"
" from the reference. Loss is only computed on the target audio segment."
msgstr ""
"来自**同一说话人**的参考音频片段路径。存在该字段时，训练序列会构造成 "
"``[103, ref_feats, 104, text, 101, audio_feats, 102]``，从而让模型学习根据参考音频克隆该说话人的声音。"
"loss 只在目标音频片段上计算。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:90 33b620a8e05249e9bee048b2c8db7614
msgid "``duration``"
msgstr "``duration``"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:92 d88ca6de723442818a1d40e1e2728088
msgid "Duration in seconds; speeds up length filtering"
msgstr "时长（秒）；可加速按长度过滤"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:93 87849c6636744aadb18fbe1d38160b03
msgid "``dataset_id``"
msgstr "``dataset_id``"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:95 271fa8c3ac144b978c13f6548594e67a
msgid "Integer ID for multi-dataset mixing (default: 0)"
msgstr "多数据集混合用的整数 ID（默认：0）"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:97 5987ddf519084e74bbf9fb2cc3774f55
msgid ""
"See ``examples/train_data_example.jsonl`` in the repository for a "
"reference."
msgstr "仓库中的 ``examples/train_data_example.jsonl`` 可供参考。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:101 a2b9fbd0722149ad8787c26ae6ce9eef
#, python-format
msgid ""
"**Mixing ref_audio and non-ref_audio samples** — We recommend that 30–50%"
" of your training samples include ``ref_audio``, so the model retains "
"both zero-shot and reference-based voice cloning abilities. A simple "
"strategy: for a given speaker, use one recording as ``ref_audio`` for the"
" next recording."
msgstr ""
"**混合使用带 ``ref_audio`` 和不带 ``ref_audio`` 的样本** —— 我们建议训练样本中有 30–50% 包含 "
"``ref_audio``，以便模型同时保留零样本和基于参考音频的声音克隆能力。一个简单策略是：对于同一说话人，可以用一段录音作为下一段录音的 "
"``ref_audio``。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:104 c09b09bb7b8e4c5a9146c91183f1330d
msgid "Audio requirements"
msgstr "音频要求"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:106 46d46dac8fbf4151824339eb6edfdf92
msgid ""
"**Format:** WAV is recommended. Other formats supported by torchaudio "
"also work."
msgstr "**格式：** 建议使用 WAV；torchaudio 支持的其它格式也可用。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:107 eacf1a2107014f21a57d35616bb0c7c1
msgid ""
"**Sample rate:** The dataloader automatically resamples to the target "
"model's rate, so you do not need to pre-resample. The ``sample_rate`` in "
"your training config must match the AudioVAE **encoder** input rate:"
msgstr ""
"**采样率：** 数据加载器会自动重采样到目标模型的采样率，一般无需预先重采样。训练配置中的 ``sample_rate`` 必须匹配 "
"AudioVAE 编码器的输入采样率："

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:109 2f87bb7caea94dc99c66c97590f27f08
msgid "VoxCPM 1.0: 16kHz"
msgstr "VoxCPM 1.0：16 kHz"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:110 477575b2e6bb47f989b1deb4363d3224
msgid "VoxCPM 1.5: 44.1kHz"
msgstr "VoxCPM 1.5：44.1 kHz"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:111 5e043ee3bfb64003ba0c72410fcf8da1
msgid "VoxCPM 2: 16kHz (the encoder operates at 16kHz; the decoder outputs 48kHz)"
msgstr "VoxCPM 2：16 kHz（编码器以 16 kHz 运行；解码器输出 48 kHz）"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:113 bc45e6906eed42a5bacf9326eecd2a30
msgid ""
"**Duration:** 3–30 seconds per clip is the practical sweet spot. Very "
"short clips (< 1s) produce unstable results. Very long clips increase "
"VRAM usage and may be filtered out by ``max_batch_tokens``."
msgstr ""
"**时长：** 每条片段 3–30 秒较为稳妥。过短（< 1 s）容易不稳定；过长会增加显存占用，并可能被 "
"``max_batch_tokens`` 过滤。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:116 c583a57afe08410983e14a00f84237e4
msgid "Preprocessing tips"
msgstr "预处理要点"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:118 e74054bf17dd43c18424279fc107a119
msgid ""
"**Trim trailing silence** to < 0.5 seconds. Long trailing silence is one "
"of the most common causes of \"generation doesn't stop\" after fine-"
"tuning."
msgstr "**去掉尾部静音**，控制在 0.5 秒以内。尾静音过长是微调后「生成停不下来」最常见原因之一。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:119 b62b7c63615242588e16e9ebc0607edc
msgid "**Normalize volume** if your recordings have inconsistent levels."
msgstr "若录音电平不一致，**请做音量归一化**。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:120 791300b659ce4a69876dc2cba1735806
msgid ""
"**Clean transcripts:** Ensure the text matches the audio exactly. "
"Mismatched text degrades both cloning quality and text adherence."
msgstr "**转写要干净：** 文本须与音频逐字一致；不匹配会同时损害克隆质量与文本贴合度。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:121 d429b131c9e9486f84c203f207296abd
msgid ""
"**Remove noisy samples.** The model is sensitive to background noise in "
"training data."
msgstr "**剔除噪声样本。** 模型对训练数据中的背景噪声较敏感。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:124 3a0e22e5a56b43ae8e6b9c8695fe024e
