#: 66487fc5a53c405ea752fbc45c9e9212 699d59354c394cdbbad8fdcb1ba6361f
msgid "**Configuration**"
msgstr "**配置**"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:166 21108b7f4910408c9e218a00f2807352
msgid "Create a YAML config file. Here is an example for VoxCPM 2:"
msgstr "请创建 YAML 配置文件。以下为 VoxCPM 2 的示例："

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:207 8c633ef9af5940218824f1ec9753f063
msgid ""
"For VoxCPM 1.5, change ``sample_rate`` to ``44100`` and "
"``pretrained_path`` to your VoxCPM 1.5 checkpoint. The ``sample_rate`` "
"must always match the AudioVAE encoder input rate in ``config.json`` — "
"**not** the output rate. The training script auto-detects the model "
"architecture from ``config.json``."
msgstr ""
"若使用 VoxCPM 1.5，请将 ``sample_rate`` 改为 ``44100``，并将 ``pretrained_path`` "
"指向你的 1.5 checkpoint。``sample_rate`` 必须始终匹配 ``config.json`` 中 AudioVAE "
"编码器的输入采样率 — 而非输出采样率。训练脚本会依据 ``config.json`` 自动识别模型结构。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:209 789ca9736d244160ab7eda9ab290bbbd
