msgstr "**启动**"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:248 1bc464bcddb4487c9e230f1ed301b3e9
msgid "**LoRA WebUI**"
msgstr "**LoRA WebUI**"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:250 ecde5ffa636a478faccd7fa8b3a54445
msgid ""
"VoxCPM also provides a Gradio UI that wraps LoRA training and inference "
"in one place:"
msgstr "VoxCPM 还提供基于 Gradio 的界面，将 LoRA 训练与推理集成在同一处："

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:257 ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:422
#: 085401857b134a179a5035d0e30066f8 3961b6f1f21d43a882a6a27a668bfef6
