msgstr "训练观察"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:259 cbaa54546831440a8b3b6e806852ecf8
msgid "Training logs to TensorBoard. Start the viewer with:"
msgstr "训练日志写入 TensorBoard。可用如下命令启动查看："

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:265 a14e4c48706e49a7bb28213045602db5
msgid "**What to watch**"
msgstr "**关注哪些指标**"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:271 225f94a039ce4265b0c4503a8edbf0c2
msgid "Metric"
msgstr "指标"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:272 bbf6108012c74b89b6f213cb67bc993d
msgid "What it tells you"
msgstr "含义"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:273 11f913cba59946cb8e51a886240f72c1
msgid "``loss/diff``"
msgstr "``loss/diff``"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:274 023378e2330947baa16cc116ea5214eb
msgid "Diffusion loss — should steadily decrease, then flatten"
msgstr "扩散损失 — 应持续下降后趋于平稳"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:275 26722fb2de864ca48b2c40ae4c848731
msgid "``loss/stop``"
msgstr "``loss/stop``"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:276 34a8fda9388f4d5b8c9cb7e1c180cfe6
msgid "Stop prediction loss — should stabilize early and stay low"
msgstr "停止预测损失 — 应较早稳定并保持较低"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:277 12d68636cd3546909858e47a3ad30275
msgid "``grad_norm``"
msgstr "``grad_norm``"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:278 56664b9066294a90b6341dcdd2fcc851
msgid ""
"Gradient magnitude — spikes may indicate bad samples or too high a "
"learning rate"
msgstr "梯度范数 — 尖峰可能表示坏样本或学习率过高"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:279 54cc9e61480c492e8495f7a509321e2d
msgid "``lr``"
msgstr "``lr``"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:280 f820746fe74d4039a37cf73dd66e22b8
msgid ""
"Learning rate curve — cosine decay with warmup, useful to verify your "
"schedule"
msgstr "学习率曲线 — 带 warm-up 的余弦衰减，可用于核对调度是否符合预期"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:282 71f64eef21654b5f9e0595606495c3b9
msgid ""
"If a validation manifest is provided, the script also logs ``val/loss`` "
"and generates sample audio + mel spectrograms in TensorBoard at each "
"``valid_interval``."
msgstr ""
"若提供验证清单，脚本还会记录 ``val/loss``，并在每个 ``valid_interval`` 在 TensorBoard "
"中生成样本音频与 mel 频谱。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:284 93884ba0fa984c39aef2b534f3fd8de2
msgid "**When to stop**"
msgstr "**何时停止**"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:286 3915b6de1ddf47ebabe612346715617b
msgid ""
"**Use epochs as a rough guide.** For single-speaker cloning, 1–3 epochs "
"are usually sufficient. Going beyond that often hurts rather than helps —"
" overfitting in TTS fine-tuning can emerge very early."
msgstr "**可把 epoch 数当作粗参考。** 单说话人克隆通常 1–3 个 epoch 足够；再往后往往弊大于利 — TTS 微调的过拟合可能很早出现。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:287 46a28dfe7ce04a1abe7b3a7cd78c1f97
msgid "``loss/diff`` plateaus and no longer decreases meaningfully."
msgstr "``loss/diff`` 进入平台期，不再有实质下降。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:288 f13c89feddb742e7ba80801e9d9a69d2
msgid "Generated audio in TensorBoard sounds good on your target voice/style."
msgstr "TensorBoard 中的生成音频在目标音色/风格上听起来已经满意。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:289 085a3f96d4484ff9becdd1feba3af411
msgid ""
"If the model starts ignoring input text (generating the same audio "
"regardless of text), you have overfit — roll back to an earlier "
"checkpoint."
msgstr "若模型开始忽略输入文本（无论输入什么都生成相似音频），即已过拟合 — 请回退到较早的 checkpoint。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:293 b5cbd5e8b4b6459b8dae5deddf976766
msgid ""
"Validation loss does not always correlate perfectly with perceptual "
"quality. Save multiple checkpoints around the convergence zone and "
"evaluate them with actual inference to pick the best one."
msgstr "验证损失与主观听感未必完全一致。建议在收敛区间附近多存几个 checkpoint，用实际推理试听后再选定最佳。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:295 ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:434
#: 3b76d9217c204962a3d0bd7ff5ce2020 faf1bbefe0624892bd5156ca0cf6144d
msgid "**Checkpoint structure**"
msgstr "**Checkpoint 目录结构**"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:310 4fffb30349484a52975c5a4b0bf62ffe
msgid ""
"Training automatically resumes from ``latest/`` if it exists. The signal "
"handler also saves a checkpoint on ``SIGTERM`` / ``SIGINT`` so you don't "
"lose progress on interruption."
msgstr ""
"若存在 ``latest/``，训练会自动从中恢复；信号处理也会在 ``SIGTERM`` / ``SIGINT`` 时保存 "
"checkpoint，避免中断丢进度。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:313 ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:454
#: 5512207db0ec48f0897c41110f0a3add 7504e0b6233645478de3e9744f1ce102
msgid "Inference"
msgstr "推理"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:315 ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:456
#: 8af11b325dc941cba7e06c86cc802943 9b967e06a0ef4c64b1553862c4378334
msgid "**CLI**"
msgstr "**命令行**"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:325 ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:473
#: 61a528d1b2b14314bd81094181d531d9 8cdc6313344f4792bcb081705a8dc630
msgid "**Python API**"
msgstr "**Python API**"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:338 9094b152c15949d4b6a7f0c7dc52566a
msgid "**Hot-swapping LoRA at runtime**"
msgstr "**运行时热切换 LoRA**"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:340 5200dde1fc624756b3b3c4296fda03d6
msgid ""
"You can load, unload, and switch LoRA weights without restarting the "
"model:"
msgstr "无需重启模型即可加载、卸载或切换 LoRA 权重："

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:357 5ab871ff276c41f68b9bb9edbbcb2c69
msgid "All hot-swap operations are compatible with ``torch.compile``."
msgstr "所有热切换操作均与 ``torch.compile`` 兼容。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:366 1fa4ce6688924bee93f923c8537c03f8
msgid ""
"Full fine-tuning updates all model parameters. Use it when LoRA does not "
"provide enough capacity — typically for new languages or large-scale "
"customization with 500+ clips."
msgstr "全量微调会更新全部参数。当 LoRA 容量不足时使用 — 常见于新语言或 500+ 条片段的大规模定制。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:402 370fb4454a37470a9b95d19a91836a75
msgid ""
"Note the ``lora`` key is absent — this tells the script to do full fine-"
"tuning."
msgstr "注意配置中不含 ``lora`` 键 — 脚本据此执行全量微调。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:404 3adc4b66d4004cd0b8447192b1c22a67
msgid "**Key differences from LoRA**"
msgstr "**与 LoRA 的主要区别**"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:406 972501a1c9cd42789f9f697ff5a8714a
msgid ""
"``learning_rate`` should be ~10x smaller (``1e-5`` vs ``1e-4``) to avoid "
"catastrophic forgetting."
msgstr "``learning_rate`` 建议约为 LoRA 的 1/10（``1e-5`` 对 ``1e-4``），以避免灾难性遗忘。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:407 c550182c694b488abc5e6d7844cc5404
msgid ""
"VRAM usage is significantly higher because all parameters require "
"gradients."
msgstr "因全部参数都参与求导，显存占用明显更高。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:408 96817dd9757d44a9983daba848389b6c
msgid "Checkpoints are larger (full model weights vs. LoRA delta only)."
msgstr "checkpoint 更大（完整权重对比仅 LoRA 增量）。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:424 b053bf1c39ed439cb66d2b5d680ede6c
msgid ""
"Same TensorBoard metrics as LoRA (``loss/diff``, ``loss/stop``, "
"``grad_norm``, ``lr``, validation audio)."
msgstr ""
"TensorBoard 指标与 LoRA 相同（``loss/diff``、`` loss/stop``、`` grad_norm``、`` "
"lr`` 及验证音频）。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:426 4d7d7734dea74550958b5dc4c4969026
msgid ""
"Full fine-tuning is more prone to overfitting than LoRA. In practice, "
"full fine-tuning often reaches its optimum within 1–2 epochs — continuing"
" beyond that can degrade quality. Pay extra attention to:"
msgstr "全量微调比 LoRA 更易过拟合。实践中常在 1–2 个 epoch 内达到较优；继续训练可能反而变差。需格外留意："

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:428 c9d5eefccea24c04b18da2da228a6cd7
msgid ""
"**Validation loss diverging from training loss** — a sign of overfitting."
" Stop and use the last checkpoint before divergence."
msgstr "**验证损失与训练损失背离** — 过拟合信号。应停止训练，并采用背离前最后一个 checkpoint。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:429 23395ec3594e46b0bd295231f3785445
msgid ""
"**Text being ignored** — the most common overfitting symptom. Keep "
"``training_cfg_rate=0.1`` (do not set it to 0) and ``weight_decay=0.01``."
" Monitor checkpoints at each ``save_interval``."
msgstr ""
"**文本被忽略** — 最常见的过拟合表现。请保持 ``training_cfg_rate=0.1`` （不要设为 0）与 `` "
"weight_decay=0.01``，并在每个 `` save_interval`` 关注 checkpoint。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:430 dccb8478448e4d0d874f48a68a4861c6
msgid ""
"**Smaller datasets overfit faster.** With fewer training samples, the "
"optimal checkpoint may appear within a few hundred steps."
msgstr "**小数据集更快过拟合。** 样本较少时，最优 checkpoint 可能出现在几百步内。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:431 31e4270a37c74cec8f5d1da5eb5cc040
msgid ""
"**New language fine-tuning:** Mix in some Chinese/English data (e.g. "
"10–20%) to reduce forgetting of the original capabilities."
msgstr "**新语言微调：** 混入部分中英数据（例如 10–20%），以减轻对原有能力的遗忘。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:432 754c700033454bc7ad2f221fdb899d01
msgid ""
"**More data does not always mean better results.** Beyond a certain "
"point, adding more data yields diminishing returns; focus on data quality"
" and diversity instead."
msgstr "**更多数据未必更好。** 超过某一点后边际收益递减；更应重视数据质量与多样性。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:451 1de83d0fd25a4835adef2aac06e09c39
msgid "Each checkpoint is a complete model directory that can be loaded directly."
msgstr "每个 checkpoint 都是可直接加载的完整模型目录。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:475 7caeeed4357343309e05fbdacb68f2d8
msgid "The checkpoint directory is a complete model — load it directly:"
msgstr "该目录即完整模型 — 可直接加载："

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:486 73bd43a8ca9145279d0817d8b0496773
msgid ""
"For common training issues (OOM, runaway generation, poor LoRA "
"performance, checkpoint errors), see :doc:`./faq`."
msgstr "常见训练问题（OOM、生成停不下来、LoRA 效果差、checkpoint 报错等）请参阅 :doc:`./faq`。"

